OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain becoming increasingly showery as
OL,7,Fwe move through the evening, however
OL,8,Fheavy bursts are still possible. Drier
OL,9,Flater in the night with some clear
OL,10,Fspells developing, these mainly
OL,11,Ftowards northeast England and
OL,12,FScotland. Remaining rather windy for
OL,13,Fmany.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FRather cloudy in the south
OL,16,Fwith patchy rain in the west. Brighter
OL,17,Ffor northern areas with showers and
OL,18,Fsome sunny spells. Winds a little
OL,19,Flighter and feeling a touch warmer.
